Formerly titled "Anonymous users cannot upload attachments to new pages using the image dialog".  Anonymous users cannot and never have been able to upload attachments to new pages. The UI should say that.
{panel}


Reproduction:
Edit space permissions so that an anonymous user can upload attachments.  

Open the Image Browser, and browse for an image file.

It will fail with the message:
{noformat}You are not permitted to attach files to this space.
{noformat}

Now try to drag and drop onto the image browser. It will fail with message:

{noformat}Attached the file 'image.png' but no thumbnail could be displayed. The file ...
{noformat}

