Open the Image dialog, and drag and drop multiple files onto it.

While the files are uploading, the progress indicator shows the % complete. AS there are multiple files, this will go up to 100% for each one, then start over.

As there is no indication of what file is currently being uploaded, this number does not really provide any useful information to the user. It should either be the % of the overall upload time, or it should also show the number of files uploaded/still to be uploaded.

